Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a different perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An imposing wall is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stopping life will lead to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you have to stop the case\Nyou've stumbled upon, Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that Unajuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta-kun, stop staring and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he get hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he must have dodged it — he seems to have passed out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, the ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it, Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it was just a simple mistake while manning the crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is an accident, not a case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And according to the nurse's station, he tripped and broke one of his legs, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing abnormal with his head or brain waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that he's still unconscious, so we can't confirm who he is or where he's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot! -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is that person's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it might have something that would reveal his identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gloves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And an envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of living."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm tired of living."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tried to commit suicide with that rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka Daijirou, 27 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he's in his 20's, he says that he's tired of living...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something a far older person would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:46.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE MAN OBSTRUCTED BY THE STEEL FRAME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You finally woke up, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, explain your circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name — it's Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't — I can't remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How sad, he doesn't know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll give him a punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you can't, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why're you stopping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may not remember now, but if he does remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might try to commit suicide again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means that I have to keep watching him, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never know when he'll get his memory back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to help him regain his memory, but, if he does, he might commit suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must solve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must solve the problem before he regains his memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants to commit suicide, because he has a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we solve it for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he won't want to die anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, this is a job for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he really lose his memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think he's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's lying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When people lie, it shows on their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll blink more, and their eyes will wander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person's eyes' were wandering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because he was worried, since he couldn't remember his own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, why would he have to lie about losing his memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's good to doubt without knowing why!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But something's off about that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when you think about it, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, he was headed south of Beika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The residential area is in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you do the opposite if you were committing suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you rather go to a mountain or something, where there aren't many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The residential area has places where there aren't many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Conan-kun doesn't want to go, we can go by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, let's investigate the problem that Manaka-san has!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, we're going to prevent his suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, prevent his suicide! Prevent his suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san's an artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not famous or anything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But these are beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all relaxing and well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a serious person, so he'll easily spend half a year finishing a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that, he can't pay his bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has trouble with money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Manaka Daijirou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you should return it to us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two million yen, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll come back later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only problem Manaka-san has is his debt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two come and ask every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the problem is debt, then the Detective Boys can't solve it, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't give up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't Manaka-san have anyone who's willing to lend him money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have any family, though he has an uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But apparently he won't even lend wisdom, no matter what he goes to ask him for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that uncle doesn't have any money, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he's loaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Ginbayashi-san – he has a mansion in Beika's South District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika's South District...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there is one, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mansion belonging to someone named Ginbayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The uncle's a family-less loner, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd think that he'd be a little more kind to his only blood relative...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His only blood relative...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A way to solve Manaka-san's debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, not that – not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what did you figure out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured out why Manaka-san was walking there at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You figured it out, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san wanted to go to his uncle's house in Beika's South District!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His goal, of course, was to take revenge for never being loaned any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted... to commit suicide there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry Mitsuhiko, but that doesn't explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What he really wanted to do was probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought you went home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this bugged me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does your foot hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The anesthesia's wearing off, so yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's good that you broke your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was your hand, you wouldn't be able to draw until you healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person knows that he's an artist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He faked his amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,' If he was interrogated by Detective Takagi, he might spill something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he faked his amnesia on the spot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san was probably heading towards his uncle Ginbayashi-san's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely just as Mitsuhiko deduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he wasn't trying to commit suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was trying to fake Ginbayashi-san's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gloves were to hide his fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suicide note's words make sense, if this was the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm tired of living."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something a far older person would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Ginbayashi-san dies, then his inheritance starts flowing to his only blood relative, Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably the motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the problem is how to explain this plot to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had to look for you, since you disappeared so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's say that there's a plan for a crime here - one that involves a person's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nothing's happened yet – it's going to happen in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving us no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you catch the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to catch the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it hasn't happened yet, then you prevent it from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We looked all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's all go and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At Ginbayashi-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that person would help with the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Manaka-san wouldn't think about doing anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime that involves a person's life – you meant a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About preventing a crime before it happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daijirou-san tried to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, he happens to have amnesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if his memory returns...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His problem is his debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you would lend money to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you still have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt that you children will understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when Daijirou graduated from college, he went to work at a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning to have him inherit my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But half a year ago, he quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to follow an old dream to become an artist
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He completely trampled all over my kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I support him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came to visit last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a man or not? You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise me that you'll quit something as stupid as painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you this, as much as you want
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Why would I depend on someone as disgusting as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you've said it, never show your face here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I'd help him, but the idiot declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the motive wasn't just money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san thought about killing this person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of his hatred from not being understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time to go to my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hinuma, prepare to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, President...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He decided to tie himself to his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:13:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let him get tied up—I don't care if he struggles or commits suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginbayashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person's eyes are wandering too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything more for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't let such a strange case happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to go see Daijirou-san in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's better to leave that idiot alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying something you don't mean again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, he lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't leave him alone, that's why every time he has an exhibition...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have me buy his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:13:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're persistent, but I'm not loaning the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were secretly buying his work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You eavesdropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you do it secretly, Manaka-san can't know that you support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't know, Manaka-san probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loathes you from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, be honest to Daijirou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't misunderstand me, Hinuma. I'm not buying his paintings to support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I buy them to burn them! ♦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where do you see those paintings I bought? There isn't even one here or at the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course there isn't, because I burned them, to illustrate how he trampled all over my kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are definitely related.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're exactly like Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your eyes wander when you lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kid... I'll kick you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a hand, Hinuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I also want to know why the president would lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What lie are you talking about? Stop, you insolent brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brat – what have you done!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you lie, there's always some evidence left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, mister, how about we go see Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell him that, in truth, you've always supported him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case will never come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that, for now, they think that I'm trying to commit suicide, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I let something slip...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't pretend to have amnesia anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tried to kill your uncle, Ginbayashi-san, with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't good; if I keep this up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, you all were trying to solve that problem for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in the end, there was only so much we could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand. Now, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he gets his memories back, I'll persuade him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"No matter how bad of a financial problem you have, you can't ever think of suicide," I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's these people – they're the debt collectors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That amnesia's gotta be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't think that I'll let you off the hook...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He heard our voices and fled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! His leg's still broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where else did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has amnesia, but he recognized the debt collector's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's the opposite! He heard the debt collector's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his memories came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he's in the dining hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If his memories came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he intend to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manaka-san disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're searching for him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one's seen him over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that he might still be in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, please come here, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His memories seems to have come back, so we need to hurry and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really might commit suicide this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're actually worried about him, aren't you!? Ginbayashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hinuma, the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, he stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he going to jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't walk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten since yesterday—I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, too, wanted to become an artist
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I couldn't make a living and, in the end, I gave up on that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you should understand Daijirou-san's hardship more than anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you mean to continue supporting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's because he understands...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That this person has been deserting Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't die, Daijirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killing yourself-you absolutely can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your memories returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, we'll listen to your story!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they listened to my story, I might let something slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'll jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found you, at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Return our two million!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay away! Neither of you come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll really jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll really, really die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic, saying "I'll die" over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you started saying that you wanted to be an artist, I opposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said that you couldn't make a living with paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, you didn't listen – you chose to live your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could someone like you understand my feelings!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, you started to depend on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Daijirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you naively think that you can keep falling back on someone whenever you're not doing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you won't be able to follow through with your dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I chose to harden my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what you requested of me, I would never support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say something so convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You secretly supported him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was buying your paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he's been buying and sending them to an elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I graduated from that elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a student's thank you card.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all the beautiful paintings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beautiful paintings always put children's hearts at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I continued to send them while holding onto that belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought my paintings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've secretly been supporting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not support!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were good paintings – they just happened to be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, he's really overdoing it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's actually a good, loving uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His eyes are wandering again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the two million.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't support, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is pre-payment for the paintings that the children are looking forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, in truth, I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ever think of suicide again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry – I'm sorry, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime that involved a person's life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We managed to prevent it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's staring again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might drop, Genta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A steel frame, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close, the saliva was about to soil my shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder?
